# Styling

This project uses Tailwind CSS for styling. 

-   Global styles can be found in the `styles/` directory.
-   Tailwind CSS configuration is in [`tailwind.config.ts`](mdc:tailwind.config.ts).
-   PostCSS configuration is in [`postcss.config.mjs`](mdc:postcss.config.mjs).
